venue.name: The Center for Arts in Natick

item.description:
Let's meetup late Sunday early evening on the deck for drinks? appetizers? a meal?
Vinny T's does have a really nice covered deck overlooking Lake Quinsig. Entertainment is the view of passing boats, maybe swimmers at the state beach across the lake

The drinks are good. If you have eaten there? The focaccia bread & roasted garlic is delicious!




_Jo
item.how_to_find_us: Ask for "Jo' & The Meetup Group- look for the meetup logo
